Interface RdbmsForeignKey

RdbmsForeignKeyImpl
public interface RdbmsForeignKey
extends RdbmsModelElement

A representation of the model object 'Rdbms Foreign Key'.

The following features are supported:

  • Rdbms Owner
  • Rdbms Refers To
  • Rdbms Column
